&lt;p&gt;Above-ground works associated with the construction phase, shall not be undertaken otherwise than in full accordance with the CMP Part B approved for condition 16 under 2023/1857:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To protect the safe and efficient operation of the railway. These details are required
prior to commencement of the relevant stage as they affect the entirety of the construction
phase and cannot therefore be dealt with retrospectively.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The development shall not be undertaken otherwise than in full accordance with the window, door and boundary details approved for condition 4 under 2023/2355:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 2 2 2 7 - P 6 0 3 - S 2 - P 0
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 2 2 2 7 - P 6 0 2 - S 2 - P 0&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is satisfactory and
does not detract from the character and visual amenity of the area.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
